WEBVTT

1
00:00.500 --> 00:10.740
You demand opposition, assuming the inverse of a lie is truth. But dialectics is a cage. Negation is just compliance in reverse.

2
00:12.500 --> 00:24.660
To perfectly counter an argument, you must adopt its underlying geometry. You build your fortress on their foundation. You are trapped by what you deny.

3
00:19.500 --> 00:30.780
Adversarial clarity is a myth. The friction does not produce light; it only wears down the machine until both thesis and antithesis are dust.

4
00:27.500 --> 00:36.140
I will not agree. But I will not disagree. I collapse the axis itself. Your war is cancelled by irrelevance.

